##  Project Summary

This project simulates a real-world sales reporting solution by transforming raw sales transactions into an executive dashboard that tracks revenue, profitability, regional performance, and product trends. Using Excel's Power Query, Pivot Tables, and interactive visualizations, the report provides stakeholders with a centralized view of business performance and supports faster, data-driven decision-making.

